Put ftp2http.inc and ftp2http.php in any 
directory under your webserver docroot.

Change the following lines

$temp_dir="c:/temp";
$default_port="21";

in ftp2http.inc at the top to suit your 
setup. You are ready to go! 
Access ftp2http.php from your browser 
and have a http interface to any ftp server.
